1
00:00:00,550 --> 00:00:01,530
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

2
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:02,560
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

3
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:18,560
[Love Upon a Time Series]

4
00:00:18,690 --> 00:00:20,110
Let me care for you

5
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:22,610
until my very last breath.

6
00:00:22,650 --> 00:00:24,840
Could you find it in your heart
to accept my love?

7
00:00:26,990 --> 00:00:28,560
Have I made myself clear?

8
00:00:43,270 --> 00:00:44,960
Dawn has not yet come.

9
00:00:45,870 --> 00:00:47,560
Let me hold you a little longer.

10
00:00:48,940 --> 00:00:51,720
Phop, it is already morning.

11
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:55,080
Even the dove in the birdhouse
has begun to coo.

12
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,260
That is not true.

13
00:01:00,210 --> 00:01:01,480
It is still quite dark outside,

14
00:01:02,580 --> 00:01:04,610
and that was an owl's cry.

15
00:01:18,430 --> 00:01:20,000
Let us remain here for but a little longer.

16
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:34,880
♫Do you know
you make me drift away into fantasy?♫

17
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:42,400
♫You've captured my heart,
and now it's yours completely♫

18
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,919
It is indeed morning, as you said.

19
00:02:10,050 --> 00:02:12,160
Even the dove in my birdhouse
has begun to coo.

20
00:02:24,490 --> 00:02:25,700
What is the matter?

21
00:02:26,530 --> 00:02:28,480
Did I hurt you so badly last night?

22
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,520
What sort of question is that?

23
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,280
Last night,

24
00:02:35,380 --> 00:02:37,079
you were very smooth, though.

25
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:39,920
It was different from what Kaew said.

26
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:42,360
You have never been involved with anyone.

27
00:02:43,530 --> 00:02:45,120
How green with jealousy you are,

28
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,000
my sweetheart.

29
00:02:56,020 --> 00:02:57,600
You are my first.

30
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:10,240
And...

31
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:12,560
Last night, why did you...

32
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:24,820
It seems you have forgotten
how much I love to read.

33
00:03:25,829 --> 00:03:27,670
Though I lack experience,

34
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:31,040
I have learned much

35
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:33,310
from the scrolls of intimacy

36
00:03:34,010 --> 00:03:35,650
and the Kama Sutra.

37
00:03:41,329 --> 00:03:41,890
Where?!

38
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,120
Where might the scrolls be?

39
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,300
Let me have a look at it!

40
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:49,570
No book can ever compare with
real experience.

41
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,520
Shall we go once more?

42
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:53,990
I shall teach you every position.

43
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,040
Stop. It is morning already!

44
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:58,360
Where are they? Show me your scrolls.

45
00:03:58,470 --> 00:03:59,360
Where are they kept?

46
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:00,960
Ow!

47
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,000
Let go! That tickles.

48
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,320
Stop... Ow.

49
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:05,440
I shall do it back to you.

50
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,600
Stop.

51
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:07,760
Ow.

52
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:10,320
Take that, take that.

53
00:04:28,470 --> 00:04:30,170
I knew how much you loved this ring,

54
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,380
so I returned to that merchant for you.

55
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,350
Wear it upon your finger always.

56
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:42,320
On our wedding day,
I shall replace it with one far more precious.

57
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:54,200
Don't touch me.

58
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:55,400
Shall we go once more?

59
00:04:55,770 --> 00:04:57,200
I told you it is morning already.

60
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:03,610
In my absence,

61
00:05:04,150 --> 00:05:06,600
keep a close watch over the servants, Bud.

62
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,160
Yes, my Lady.

63
00:05:08,460 --> 00:05:11,720
I shall keep watch with utmost care,
to ensure no dishonor comes to our house.

64
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:21,120
Phop,

65
00:05:22,710 --> 00:05:24,840
be diligent in teaching your brother.

66
00:05:25,050 --> 00:05:26,600
Waste no time playing around.

67
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:28,320
Yes, Mother.

68
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,409
Let us depart.

69
00:05:41,909 --> 00:05:43,720
There is no need
for a fussy farewell at the pier.

70
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:49,320
Resolve at once the matter
of the culprits smuggling contraband.

71
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:51,840
Upon my return from Song Khwae,

72
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:54,780
you must accompany me to Lavo

73
00:05:55,620 --> 00:05:57,159
to seek Lady Varna's hand in marriage.

74
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:16,480
It is seldom that
His Excellency is seen bearing his sword.

75
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:18,160
He looks rather majestic, does he not, Sai?

76
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,040
Indeed.

77
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:32,310
[Love Upon a Time Series]

78
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:46,040
[Love Upon a Time Series]

79
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,820
Make haste. Be quick.

80
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,810
Hey, hey, hey!

81
00:07:54,530 --> 00:07:55,500
Chuay!

82
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,800
Chuay.

83
00:07:58,050 --> 00:07:59,360
- Chuay!
- What is it?!

84
00:08:14,740 --> 00:08:16,180
I bought this plant

85
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,870
so that we may nurture it together.

86
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:20,800
When it blossoms and bears fruit,

87
00:08:20,980 --> 00:08:22,310
we shall together admire its beauty.

88
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,360
I love him.

89
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:03,480
I love him not.

90
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,680
I love him.

91
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:06,040
Of course, I love him.

92
00:09:08,370 --> 00:09:09,360
Chuay.

93
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,840
I have already told you
my illness has passed.

94
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,700
You need not keep watch over me
by my bedside.

95
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,820
I am not here
to watch over your bedside, Master Klao.

96
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,700
I am here to share your bed.

97
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,200
Phop!

98
00:09:20,210 --> 00:09:20,810
Hey.

99
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,610
I shall tell Lord Phop that

100
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:24,560
a thief...

101
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:28,400
broke into my quarters and kissed my cheek.

102
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:30,360
In that case,

103
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:34,080
may I accept my punishment
in the form of a kiss?

104
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:41,760
Take that.

105
00:09:42,050 --> 00:09:43,040
Smells pleasant, does it not?

106
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:44,580
No.

107
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,590
Your cheek smells far more pleasant.

108
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,280
Hey!

109
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,080
Hey, don't...

110
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,920
What manner of snack is this?

111
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,140
I have never seen it before.

112
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,840
It is a snack from Phichit.

113
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:56,960
I taught Muan how to make it.

114
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:59,920
But this is for myself alone.

115
00:10:00,310 --> 00:10:01,640
You must not take it from me.

116
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,800
Phop, the servants saw that.

117
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,640
Let them witness it.

118
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,000
Tonight...

119
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:42,700
stay in my quarters
for one more night, Klao.

120
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:50,000
I wish His Excellency and our Lady
would stay away a little longer.

121
00:10:50,210 --> 00:10:51,690
Master Klao and our lord

122
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,320
are most happy together.

123
00:11:24,770 --> 00:11:26,390
Have I told you

124
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,510
that I love you?

125
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:32,830
You have, countless times.

126
00:11:33,710 --> 00:11:35,760
Yet I always wish to hear it once more.

127
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:39,460
I love you.

128
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,730
I love you dearly.

129
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,200
Be gentle,

130
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,080
or the war elephant
will yearn for another war.

131
00:12:15,130 --> 00:12:17,360
Conceal your ambitions at times, I pray.

132
00:12:18,070 --> 00:12:21,080
Even now,
the servants gossip of nothing else.

133
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:27,300
Speaking of gossip,

134
00:12:28,570 --> 00:12:30,240
have you ever wondered

135
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:32,040
why is it that Cherd

136
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:35,040
can track me wherever I go?

137
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:37,600
It is as if he foreknows

138
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:40,280
both my destination

139
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:41,590
and the moment I shall depart.

140
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:48,040
The night prior,
at the Pavilion of Affection...

141
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,400
Word from your manor

142
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:53,880
says that you have changed,
as if you were a different person.

143
00:12:54,830 --> 00:12:56,630
He spoke as though

144
00:12:58,370 --> 00:13:00,240
someone within our own manor
had a loose tongue.

145
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:04,320
Whom do you suspect?

146
00:13:06,130 --> 00:13:09,520
The servants in our manor
are entirely trustworthy.

147
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:12,600
I do not think it is one of the servants.

148
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:16,700
Perhaps it is...

149
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,200
- Lady Bud.
- Aunt Bud.

150
00:13:28,690 --> 00:13:29,560
What was that?

151
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:33,520
You claimed that Klao borrowed your garments
to attire himself as a woman?

152
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:35,120
Was he attiring himself
for an affair of love?

153
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,880
Oh!

154
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,360
Good heavens!
I think that was not the case.

155
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:41,640
It would seem he dressed for a play,

156
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:44,920
though I believe he disguised himself
to investigate certain matters.

157
00:13:45,140 --> 00:13:46,400
I certainly think you are wrong.

158
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,410
Do you truly think so?

159
00:13:47,450 --> 00:13:49,080
Then how else am I meant to think?

160
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,320
- Oh...
- But that...

161
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:51,370
That was how it went.

162
00:13:51,530 --> 00:13:52,530
Lady Euang.

163
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:54,730
Oh!

164
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,880
Handsome one,

165
00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:58,350
you have returned again.

166
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,200
How did it fare?

167
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:02,720
As I told you last time,

168
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:04,880
did you find Klao there?

169
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:06,610
I did,

170
00:14:07,110 --> 00:14:09,640
but he ran into the House of Pleasure.

171
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,770
What think you, Lady Euang?

172
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:16,000
Is he in search of the truth
of his own past?

173
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:18,110
Hm...

174
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,240
That I know not.

175
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:23,710
But these days, he speaks with
far more sense than he did before.

176
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:26,840
I believe some of his memories
have returned to him.

177
00:14:30,930 --> 00:14:32,000
At this very moment,

178
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,880
what is it that he schemes to do?

179
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:47,600
Uh...

180
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:55,080
He is troubled by
the illicit taking of opium.

181
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:59,420
He is seeking the one who...

182
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,220
This one.

183
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:03,420
I want it.

184
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:05,610
Oh, by all means.

185
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:14,000
I wish to take them all.

186
00:15:14,530 --> 00:15:15,070
All of these.

187
00:15:18,740 --> 00:15:19,940
Thank you.

188
00:15:59,630 --> 00:16:02,400
Wounded as he is,
he could not have fled far.

189
00:16:03,110 --> 00:16:05,210
Have you searched for this man thoroughly

190
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:06,440
at the market,

191
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:09,160
the opium den,
and the House of Pleasure?

192
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:13,160
Certainly, Lord Phop.

193
00:16:14,260 --> 00:16:15,770
Such matters require time.

194
00:16:16,690 --> 00:16:17,920
Why must you be in such perilous haste?

195
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,220
Dear Klao witnessed the bandits

196
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,720
in the act of stealing the seized goods.

197
00:16:23,090 --> 00:16:25,800
The culprits knew where the keys
and contraband were hidden.

198
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,120
Perchance

199
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:31,010
the mastermind behind this affair
lies within the department itself.

200
00:16:42,470 --> 00:16:43,420
Are you certain of this?

201
00:16:45,470 --> 00:16:46,600
But has Dear Klao

202
00:16:47,310 --> 00:16:49,230
recovered from his madness
and his loss of memory?

203
00:16:50,190 --> 00:16:52,250
He speaks with far greater sense
and reason than before.

204
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,910
I believe he can be trusted now.

205
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:58,880
If such is the case,

206
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:02,340
we must pursue the truth
with even greater caution.

207
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:03,990
No one can be trusted.

208
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:13,000
Lord Phop,

209
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:17,480
you must never speak of
this matter here again.

210
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:23,560
I must go upon patrol now.

211
00:17:45,410 --> 00:17:47,040
I told my client that I required the privy.

212
00:17:48,060 --> 00:17:50,120
I have but a fleeting moment
to spare for you, Cherd.

213
00:17:50,910 --> 00:17:52,100
This is already plenty.

214
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:02,810
What matter brought Klao
to seek you out the other night?

215
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,010
What else could it be?

216
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:10,000
He came seeking

217
00:18:12,620 --> 00:18:13,960
my beauty, of course.

218
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:16,520
Trifle not with me.

219
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:18,120
Answer me,

220
00:18:18,630 --> 00:18:19,640
or I shall...

221
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:21,120
Or you shall what?

222
00:18:22,740 --> 00:18:25,640
With but a single cry from me,

223
00:18:26,850 --> 00:18:28,210
the patrolmen outside

224
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:30,040
shall be upon you at once.

225
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,720
You are fleeing from them, are you not?

226
00:18:43,120 --> 00:18:43,760
Ouch!

227
00:18:43,930 --> 00:18:44,570
Ow!!

228
00:18:47,870 --> 00:18:48,870
You are wounded also.

229
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:50,560
What was it that you did?

230
00:18:50,730 --> 00:18:51,800
Silence!

231
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,160
Answer me this instant.

232
00:18:54,840 --> 00:18:56,820
For what matter did Klao seek you out?

233
00:18:57,410 --> 00:18:58,400
What was it that he knew?

234
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:00,790
Well...

235
00:19:04,590 --> 00:19:08,010
He knows nothing of
your opium meeting place.

236
00:19:18,010 --> 00:19:19,000
Hand over that ring at once.

237
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:25,600
The next time

238
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,800
he comes to seek me,

239
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:31,800
I may perchance let it slip.

240
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:40,110
Then you may cease this jealousy,
for we both know...

241
00:19:41,050 --> 00:19:44,350
you are simply terrified that
I have at last learned the truth about you.

242
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:55,370
Should your tongue slip,
I shall bring about your demise.

243
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:57,600
You would not dare.

244
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,400
But my master surely would.

245
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:05,410
We shall see
if you can keep up this bravery, Pim.

246
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:13,800
Hold, my Lady.

247
00:20:14,930 --> 00:20:15,960
Who is that man?

248
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:17,870
Has he in any way harmed you?

249
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:21,040
It was nothing.

250
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:22,960
He merely mistook me for another.

251
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:25,180
I shall take my leave now.

252
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:47,400
Were you a lady, Master Kaew,

253
00:20:47,770 --> 00:20:51,680
I dare say your charms would captivate
the hearts of every gentleman.

254
00:21:19,210 --> 00:21:21,600
And now,
the batter is ready for frying, Klao.

255
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:25,400
Pray allow me to attend to
this matter myself, Masters.

256
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:27,950
If we leave the frying to Master Klao,

257
00:21:28,210 --> 00:21:30,310
I fear Lord Phop will have returned
before it is done.

258
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,860
Else this would spoil the surprise.

259
00:21:34,290 --> 00:21:34,800
Come.

260
00:21:37,630 --> 00:21:38,860
Good heavens!

261
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:42,240
You did not tell me
this batch of khanom kong was meant for Phop.

262
00:21:43,150 --> 00:21:44,760
I ought not to have taken this job from you.

263
00:21:45,610 --> 00:21:47,120
Pay it no mind, Kaew.

264
00:21:48,260 --> 00:21:50,700
To see you smile

265
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:52,320
and cook once more

266
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:53,840
already delights me.

267
00:21:56,770 --> 00:21:58,880
I only did as you taught me,

268
00:21:59,450 --> 00:22:00,920
which was to love myself more,

269
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:04,200
so that I would never have to cry
over him again.

270
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:09,480
I have prepared
this meal for you today, you see.

271
00:22:13,630 --> 00:22:14,400
Here.

272
00:22:18,910 --> 00:22:19,960
Oh.

273
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:23,400
Do you often bring me meals like this?

274
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:25,640
Not at all, Master.

275
00:22:25,910 --> 00:22:28,240
It is his usual practice
to prepare it for the Physician each day.

276
00:22:28,330 --> 00:22:30,320
- But after...
- Buaphan!

277
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:34,900
Have I not told you
to speak of him no more?

278
00:22:37,100 --> 00:22:38,200
Or else,

279
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:40,320
I shall move to Pak Nam Pho
the very next day.

280
00:22:43,340 --> 00:22:44,280
Hm...

281
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:47,710
You once prepared it for Jom
every single day,

282
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,000
but now that this has come to pass,

283
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,920
I wonder how he fares.

284
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,120
He would likely fare well enough without me.

285
00:23:00,150 --> 00:23:02,340
Let him feast on dried herbs

286
00:23:02,950 --> 00:23:04,440
and live on his remedies.

287
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:07,020
Klao!

288
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:08,960
Dear Klao!!

289
00:23:09,710 --> 00:23:11,000
Has Kaew come to this manor?!!

290
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:51,680
How utterly heartless of you.

291
00:23:51,770 --> 00:23:53,640
You stopped bringing food to my manor

292
00:23:53,930 --> 00:23:55,180
and gave it all to Klao?

293
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:56,320
You deserve it, do you not?

294
00:23:57,830 --> 00:23:59,640
Who was it that behaved heartlessly first?

295
00:24:15,310 --> 00:24:16,340
Forgive me.

296
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:23,000
Do not journey to Pak Nam Pho, Kaew.

297
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,320
I sought you at your manor,

298
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:27,660
and upon not finding you there,

299
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:30,960
my heart burned with restless unease.

300
00:24:35,980 --> 00:24:38,800
Should you truly leave,
I fear I could no longer bear this life.

301
00:24:41,730 --> 00:24:43,430
But do you not find me tiresome?

302
00:24:45,290 --> 00:24:47,000
Do you not wish me gone?

303
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:48,160
Not anymore.

304
00:24:48,990 --> 00:24:51,200
My only wish now
is to have you by my side, Kaew.

305
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:57,320
I am well aware of the wrongs
I have done to you.

306
00:24:58,160 --> 00:25:00,330
You may find it in your heart
not to forgive me.

307
00:25:02,210 --> 00:25:03,720
Yet I beg you to grant me another chance.

308
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:08,760
From this day forth,
I shall cherish you with the utmost care,

309
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:11,800
that I may atone for the wrongs of my past.

310
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:24,330
How can I remain by your side,

311
00:25:27,110 --> 00:25:29,090
and what would I be to you, Jom?

312
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:35,920
Even that, you cannot answer.

313
00:25:42,230 --> 00:25:43,040
Just eat,

314
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:45,600
for you have gone without food
for far too long.

315
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:51,000
From this day forth, I shall have
my servants deliver meals to your manor.

316
00:25:51,690 --> 00:25:52,890
That shall suffice.

317
00:26:03,910 --> 00:26:04,710
Kaew...

318
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:05,940
I am truly sorry.

319
00:26:09,450 --> 00:26:10,860
I beg you to grant me another chance.

320
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:11,790
Kaew...

321
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:13,150
Kaew.

322
00:26:18,690 --> 00:26:19,820
Kaew, forgive me.

323
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:25,200
Pray forgive me, Kaew.

324
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:28,870
One more chance, Kaew. I beg of you.

325
00:26:44,630 --> 00:26:46,080
Oh! Phop.

326
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:47,400
You have returned?

327
00:26:50,700 --> 00:26:51,910
If I have not,

328
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,090
who then kissed you?

329
00:26:55,210 --> 00:26:56,160
Muan, was it?

330
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:05,280
Are our Good Physician
and Kaew at our manor?

331
00:27:07,410 --> 00:27:08,620
Have the two reconciled?

332
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,920
Matters are still far from well.

333
00:27:15,320 --> 00:27:16,840
It is not easy for Kaew.

334
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,160
He has suffered much pain.

335
00:27:22,060 --> 00:27:23,680
It is not for Jom either.

336
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,640
He is a physician,

337
00:27:27,460 --> 00:27:29,520
highly respected by many.

338
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:35,430
Even to admit the truth to himself
is difficult enough.

339
00:27:43,350 --> 00:27:44,880
I can never thank you enough

340
00:27:46,090 --> 00:27:47,400
for facing your own heart

341
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:49,540
and having the will to keep me by your side.

342
00:28:02,670 --> 00:28:05,560
And I shall be by your side,
now and forevermore.

343
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:16,640
I am sorry, Kaew.

344
00:28:18,210 --> 00:28:19,390
Pray give me a chance.

345
00:28:20,140 --> 00:28:22,080
- I am sorry.
- Then answer me.

346
00:28:23,130 --> 00:28:24,740
You cannot even answer that.

347
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:28,850
If I find out

348
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:31,460
who the true culprit is,

349
00:28:32,080 --> 00:28:34,010
I will probably be sent back to the present.

350
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:35,570
If that is so,

351
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:37,750
I will not be able to be with Phop.

352
00:28:42,130 --> 00:28:44,120
Should we not pursue the truth,

353
00:28:44,900 --> 00:28:48,000
we shall never be able to clear
my father's name from the past life.

354
00:28:58,360 --> 00:28:59,130
See?

355
00:28:59,910 --> 00:29:01,860
Now that I realize
I am the same person as Klao,

356
00:29:02,250 --> 00:29:04,520
even my thoughts have taken on
this archaic tone.

357
00:29:12,410 --> 00:29:14,340
Muan said you prepared this for me yourself.

358
00:29:17,660 --> 00:29:18,540
It is divine.

359
00:29:29,770 --> 00:29:31,950
Is there any way to solve the mystery

360
00:29:32,690 --> 00:29:34,640
without leaving him behind?

361
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:47,720
What is this?

362
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:49,820
You always spend all your time with it.

363
00:29:49,850 --> 00:29:50,420
Hey!

364
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:53,780
Phop, give me that!

365
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:55,120
Give it to me.

366
00:29:55,660 --> 00:29:56,410
Hand it over!

367
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:58,400
Let me see it
so that my doubts may be laid to rest.

368
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:12,440
Phop.

369
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:15,480
Give it to me.

370
00:30:15,540 --> 00:30:17,400
Do not, Phop. I am ticklish.

371
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:23,360
A record of the case,

372
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:26,040
written in Farangi script.

373
00:30:26,990 --> 00:30:28,370
I cannot make sense of it.

374
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,980
Why do you withhold it from me?

375
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:36,480
You promised
you would share every matter with me.

376
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:44,420
There are certain things I cannot show you.

377
00:30:53,430 --> 00:30:55,310
You truly have a fondness
for drawing, do you not?

378
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:01,330
What creature did you illustrate?

379
00:31:03,320 --> 00:31:04,470
Is it a crocodile

380
00:31:06,210 --> 00:31:07,440
or a monitor lizard?

381
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:09,790
Gosh!

382
00:31:09,810 --> 00:31:10,920
It is no monitor lizard.

383
00:31:11,990 --> 00:31:13,440
Stop asking and give it back!

384
00:31:18,300 --> 00:31:19,280
What about this?

385
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:21,160
What is this emblem?

386
00:31:21,570 --> 00:31:22,680
A sacred fig leaf?

387
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,240
Do you have a fondness
for this kind of leaf?

388
00:31:31,320 --> 00:31:33,230
Farangi writing.

389
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,080
What does this signify?

390
00:31:36,700 --> 00:31:38,170
It reads...

391
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,320
"Ei-luv-yu."

392
00:31:40,860 --> 00:31:42,240
It means...

393
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:44,000
"I love you."

394
00:31:45,290 --> 00:31:46,240
You know what it means?

395
00:31:50,180 --> 00:31:51,160
It was a guess.

396
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:55,640
It is evident that
this creature resembles me.

397
00:31:57,010 --> 00:31:59,180
As for this grumpy-looking cat,

398
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:03,060
it does rather resemble you.

399
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:11,120
The monitor lizard is depicted as
wanting to give the grumpy cat a kiss.

400
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,740
I shall eat every last bite.

401
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:43,560
I would even swallow the banana leaves.

402
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,380
Never in all my life

403
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:53,760
has anyone done such a thing for me,

404
00:32:54,580 --> 00:32:55,800
not even my mother.

405
00:32:59,130 --> 00:33:00,360
Never in all my life,

406
00:33:00,730 --> 00:33:02,570
have I done such a thing for anyone.

407
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:29,560
Pray return to me soon, my Phop.

408
00:33:30,490 --> 00:33:31,200
Certainly.

409
00:33:31,570 --> 00:33:33,440
I shall thoroughly look into the matter

410
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:35,120
as we have discussed.

411
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,980
Pray wait for my return at the manor.

412
00:33:39,890 --> 00:33:41,800
Do not wander elsewhere.

413
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:43,480
Certainly.

414
00:33:51,910 --> 00:33:53,920
It is not only the manor that has changed.

415
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:55,650
In these past few days alone,

416
00:33:55,870 --> 00:33:58,160
you yourself
have likewise changed greatly.

417
00:34:00,250 --> 00:34:01,440
- Suddenly...
- Good heavens!

418
00:34:01,620 --> 00:34:04,310
you no longer speak as a man from Phichit.

419
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:06,960
You also attend to the cares
of the household,

420
00:34:07,210 --> 00:34:09,679
harbor no desire to venture outside,

421
00:34:09,810 --> 00:34:12,300
and are thoroughly content

422
00:34:12,770 --> 00:34:15,120
in both body and mind, Master.

423
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,310
Indeed, it is so.

424
00:34:21,190 --> 00:34:21,900
But...

425
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:25,159
Uncle and Aunt
are to return this evening.

426
00:34:26,830 --> 00:34:28,760
Yet I see no harm in such a matter.

427
00:34:30,179 --> 00:34:31,960
The morrow has not yet arrived.

428
00:34:32,100 --> 00:34:33,840
What is wrong,
then, with simply being happy today?

429
00:34:48,889 --> 00:34:49,679
Good heavens!

430
00:34:50,510 --> 00:34:52,400
Has our Good Aunt not yet returned?

431
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,770
Your journey here is but in vain.

432
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:04,960
In the end...

433
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:09,420
you have only come to help me
arrange these crown flowers into pots for Phop.

434
00:35:11,700 --> 00:35:12,680
This is indeed good.

435
00:35:12,830 --> 00:35:15,540
To be able to make something for the Lord,

436
00:35:15,980 --> 00:35:17,160
I am more than glad to do this.

437
00:35:22,540 --> 00:35:23,720
Lady Varna,

438
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:26,890
do you truly love Phop to such an extent?

439
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:33,340
To call it "love" might be overstated.

440
00:35:34,250 --> 00:35:35,250
I...

441
00:35:35,650 --> 00:35:38,240
I cannot claim to know him
to such a degree.

442
00:35:38,960 --> 00:35:39,600
Yet...

443
00:35:41,370 --> 00:35:43,160
you are soon to be wedded to him.

444
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:47,680
Since the elders have decreed as such,

445
00:35:48,640 --> 00:35:52,400
how could I possibly raise any objection?

446
00:35:58,970 --> 00:35:59,840
Then...

447
00:36:00,570 --> 00:36:01,760
To speak truthfully,

448
00:36:03,170 --> 00:36:04,880
what is it that you want, Lady Varna?

449
00:36:05,620 --> 00:36:07,120
Or what is it that you want to be?

450
00:36:16,010 --> 00:36:17,680
I...

451
00:36:25,160 --> 00:36:26,680
I truly do not know.

452
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:31,570
No one has ever asked me that until now.

453
00:36:35,300 --> 00:36:36,120
Uh...

454
00:36:37,470 --> 00:36:38,680
Since my birth,

455
00:36:39,750 --> 00:36:41,920
I have been but my father's daughter.

456
00:36:43,330 --> 00:36:44,520
When I come of age,

457
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:46,640
I must wed

458
00:36:47,310 --> 00:36:49,060
and become a wife.

459
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:51,600
Such is all I have ever known.

460
00:36:58,850 --> 00:36:59,400
And...

461
00:36:59,910 --> 00:37:00,890
Lady Varna...

462
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:02,440
What is it that you take pleasure in doing?

463
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:11,470
I am fond of floral crafts

464
00:37:13,410 --> 00:37:14,410
and...

465
00:37:15,150 --> 00:37:16,570
handicrafts,

466
00:37:17,210 --> 00:37:19,760
as you are, perhaps.

467
00:37:22,790 --> 00:37:24,800
I am fond of the capital.

468
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:26,790
Here,

469
00:37:27,290 --> 00:37:29,360
it is adorned with such beauty,

470
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:32,470
and there is no lack of pleasures to pursue.

471
00:37:35,410 --> 00:37:36,340
High Lord Soontrapinit,

472
00:37:36,850 --> 00:37:38,500
father to Lord Harn,

473
00:37:38,530 --> 00:37:39,800
once told me that

474
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,040
if I were to...

475
00:37:42,650 --> 00:37:45,200
wed Lord Phop,

476
00:37:46,310 --> 00:37:48,000
I might be able to settle here
in the capital.

477
00:37:49,370 --> 00:37:51,640
I would no longer have to return
and be alone in Lavo.

478
00:38:16,100 --> 00:38:18,050
You are free to pursue
that which brings you joy,

479
00:38:19,470 --> 00:38:20,470
be it a lady of the court

480
00:38:21,860 --> 00:38:23,780
or a lady-in-waiting,
and to stand upon your own feet.

481
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,310
Or...

482
00:38:26,830 --> 00:38:28,010
follow your heart

483
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,960
in working with flowers.

484
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:39,080
You were born a lady in your own right,

485
00:38:40,450 --> 00:38:44,050
bound not to be merely someone's daughter

486
00:38:44,470 --> 00:38:46,950
or someone's wife.

487
00:38:49,270 --> 00:38:51,200
Your worth, Lady Varna,
is far greater than that.

488
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:48,440
Lord Phop.

489
00:39:48,870 --> 00:39:50,680
The meeting place for the opium smuggling

490
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,640
was recorded in the notes
in a foreign script.

491
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:55,000
What manner of peculiarity is this?

492
00:39:55,680 --> 00:39:58,840
It is connected to
his previous disappearance.

493
00:39:59,720 --> 00:40:01,750
Were that location of no significance,

494
00:40:02,300 --> 00:40:04,170
such a dire fate
would never have befallen Klao.

495
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:06,840
The fifteenth night of the waning moon.

496
00:40:07,530 --> 00:40:09,120
The second period.

497
00:40:09,850 --> 00:40:12,240
The abandoned hut by the pond,

498
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:15,090
deep within the woods of Wat Sema.

499
00:40:15,780 --> 00:40:16,680
This must be it.

500
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:20,650
Before suffering from amnesia,

501
00:40:22,610 --> 00:40:25,160
I discovered the location
of the opium meeting place.

502
00:40:25,780 --> 00:40:27,160
Thus, I recorded it.

503
00:40:29,620 --> 00:40:32,210
Why have I not asked for your help sooner?

504
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:37,380
That is so.

505
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:39,590
Why have you not asked me?

506
00:40:42,870 --> 00:40:43,880
Uh...

507
00:40:44,310 --> 00:40:46,290
At that time,

508
00:40:46,330 --> 00:40:48,680
I had not yet regained my memories.

509
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:53,280
Thus, I could not bring myself
to tell you everything.

510
00:40:55,170 --> 00:40:56,640
Oh, Phop.

511
00:40:57,750 --> 00:40:58,840
Perchance,

512
00:40:59,370 --> 00:41:02,000
within that very place,
there may lie the crucial evidence

513
00:41:02,930 --> 00:41:04,500
revealing the mastermind behind this.

514
00:41:08,110 --> 00:41:08,920
Of course.

515
00:41:09,430 --> 00:41:11,120
I shall look into this matter.

516
00:41:16,750 --> 00:41:18,440
However, there remains one issue.

517
00:41:20,990 --> 00:41:23,240
Which Wat Sema is it?

518
00:41:25,080 --> 00:41:27,640
The nearest temples are
Wat Sema Muang, Wat Sema Khu,

519
00:41:27,860 --> 00:41:29,160
and Wat Sema Thong.

520
00:41:30,300 --> 00:41:33,600
It would be best to deploy the patrol units
in order to search all three temples.

521
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:38,780
Lord Phop.

522
00:41:39,700 --> 00:41:42,310
Klao's note is but proof without its origin.

523
00:41:43,130 --> 00:41:45,180
It is not sufficient
to justify the mobilization of the patrol units.

524
00:41:46,930 --> 00:41:49,640
Ascertain first which temple it is.

525
00:41:50,470 --> 00:41:51,760
Then we shall discuss this further.

526
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:08,630
Cherd has been at Thong's tavern all day.

527
00:42:09,090 --> 00:42:10,200
Pray, set your mind at ease.

528
00:42:10,390 --> 00:42:11,320
Good.

529
00:42:11,520 --> 00:42:14,560
What of the records
for Lord Preechapiban's case?

530
00:42:15,450 --> 00:42:16,960
I have searched everywhere.

531
00:42:17,410 --> 00:42:19,060
Yet the opium trading permit you seek

532
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:20,160
cannot be found.

533
00:42:25,710 --> 00:42:26,770
How can this be?

534
00:42:29,310 --> 00:42:30,660
Search within the city as well.

535
00:42:30,850 --> 00:42:32,360
Someone may be keeping it hidden there.

536
00:42:32,510 --> 00:42:33,220
Yes, my Lord.

537
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:11,920
♫Sometimes I find myself
whispering your name♫

538
00:43:11,960 --> 00:43:16,120
♫In sleep, I see you in my reveries♫

539
00:43:16,200 --> 00:43:23,210
♫In my heart, the wishes are all for you♫

540
00:43:24,420 --> 00:43:28,480
♫And whenever a shooting star falls,
I make a wish♫

541
00:43:28,550 --> 00:43:32,580
♫From memories sweet to the days yet to be,♫

542
00:43:32,650 --> 00:43:39,660
♫May no harm or sorrow ever come near you♫

543
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:43,880
♫I don't always know if the prayers that I make♫

544
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:47,950
♫Are the ones your heart would want to take♫

545
00:43:48,190 --> 00:43:55,970
♫What am I to do
when my heart may never change?♫

546
00:43:56,000 --> 00:43:59,640
♫Still thinking of you and only you♫

547
00:43:59,690 --> 00:44:04,260
♫The thought of your tears
is what frightens me♫

548
00:44:04,290 --> 00:44:12,530
♫Wishing rains and skies
never take your smile away♫

549
00:44:12,560 --> 00:44:21,540
♫Every plea I make, please let it reach you♫

550
00:44:21,580 --> 00:44:25,840
♫Don't leave this heart lost in worry and plea♫

551
00:44:25,870 --> 00:44:29,510
♫Please take care of it for me♫

552
00:44:30,590 --> 00:44:33,250
Lady Varna, I hope you come to know

553
00:44:33,520 --> 00:44:36,500
who you wish to be and what you wish to achieve.

554
00:44:47,450 --> 00:44:48,240
Klao!

555
00:44:48,960 --> 00:44:50,240
Where is my child?

556
00:44:50,940 --> 00:44:52,960
Where have you taken Orn and my child away?

557
00:44:53,650 --> 00:44:54,640
Pray, wait a moment.

558
00:44:55,060 --> 00:44:56,080
Aunt Bud and Aunt Euang,

559
00:44:56,650 --> 00:44:58,600
I was with Lady Varna all afternoon.

560
00:44:59,270 --> 00:45:00,520
I know nothing.

561
00:45:01,140 --> 00:45:02,080
What has happened?

562
00:45:02,540 --> 00:45:03,640
Have your children disappeared?

563
00:45:04,070 --> 00:45:05,120
Obviously.

564
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:07,080
My servant told me that

565
00:45:07,200 --> 00:45:08,440
your friend came for a visit.

566
00:45:09,130 --> 00:45:11,080
Boon and Orn came to play with that person,

567
00:45:11,530 --> 00:45:13,510
but soon after, three of them disappeared.

568
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:15,260
My friend?

569
00:45:16,340 --> 00:45:17,760
Do you refer to Jom and Kaew?

570
00:45:17,990 --> 00:45:18,720
No, I am not.

571
00:45:19,720 --> 00:45:20,730
My servant said that

572
00:45:20,750 --> 00:45:23,280
this person bears a grievous wound
upon the left arm.

573
00:45:24,030 --> 00:45:25,640
Who is this friend of yours?

574
00:45:28,710 --> 00:45:30,840
A grievous wound upon the left arm.

575
00:45:36,430 --> 00:45:40,280
♫Wat Bot, oh, the temple of old,♫

576
00:45:42,030 --> 00:45:46,360
♫Where seven toddy palms stand tall as told♫

577
00:45:48,770 --> 00:45:54,420
♫Khun Thong went forth on the raid♫

578
00:45:55,990 --> 00:46:02,920
♫Still, he has yet to return
for the sweet embrace♫

579
00:46:03,100 --> 00:46:07,680
♫Wrapping food in a bundle,♫

580
00:46:08,800 --> 00:46:13,210
♫I rowed out to look for my angel♫

581
00:46:14,860 --> 00:46:18,980
♫Yet the rumors had already spread♫

582
00:46:21,230 --> 00:46:24,080
♫That Khun Thong had met♫

583
00:46:25,060 --> 00:46:28,840
♫His fate♫

584
00:46:31,240 --> 00:46:32,040
Cherd!!

585
00:46:33,750 --> 00:46:35,080
You did not spare even children?!!

586
00:46:35,270 --> 00:46:36,760
You are but scum of the earth!!

587
00:46:37,420 --> 00:46:38,200
Hey!!

588
00:46:41,830 --> 00:46:43,720
Brother Klao,
why must you hurt Brother Cherd?

589
00:46:43,990 --> 00:46:45,560
He played with me.

590
00:46:45,900 --> 00:46:47,680
And sang me a lullaby.

591
00:46:49,480 --> 00:46:50,400
Good heavens!

592
00:46:51,330 --> 00:46:52,690
There is no need to lay blame upon him.

593
00:46:52,730 --> 00:46:54,160
He simply is not fond of me.

594
00:46:59,730 --> 00:47:02,440
That is enough playing for today.

595
00:47:02,720 --> 00:47:05,360
Return to the manor at once
lest your mothers become anxious.

596
00:47:07,280 --> 00:47:08,680
Off with the charade.

597
00:47:11,230 --> 00:47:11,920
Ouch!

598
00:47:13,380 --> 00:47:14,780
Your arm is wounded.

599
00:47:16,370 --> 00:47:18,640
So, you truly were trying
to seize the contraband.

600
00:47:18,690 --> 00:47:20,080
Ouch! It hurts!

601
00:47:20,140 --> 00:47:21,600
Boon and Orn, I need your help!

602
00:47:21,840 --> 00:47:23,760
Ow! Help me, please!

603
00:47:24,520 --> 00:47:25,260
Boon.

604
00:47:25,720 --> 00:47:26,480
Ow!!

605
00:47:43,380 --> 00:47:45,280
You intended to lure me here to my demise,

606
00:47:46,490 --> 00:47:49,220
for the plot at that hut failed, did you not?

607
00:47:55,600 --> 00:47:56,710
You truly have regained memories?

608
00:48:01,980 --> 00:48:05,860
So, the rumors that you are seeking the truth
are indeed true.

609
00:48:06,780 --> 00:48:07,510
Yes.

610
00:48:09,370 --> 00:48:10,400
And

611
00:48:11,100 --> 00:48:13,670
I am drawing closer to it
with every passing moment.

612
00:48:16,820 --> 00:48:18,920
I shall not grant mercy to you or your master.

613
00:48:23,880 --> 00:48:24,600
Klao.

614
00:48:27,700 --> 00:48:28,680
Are you injured?

615
00:48:32,740 --> 00:48:33,940
Leave this ground at once,

616
00:48:34,720 --> 00:48:36,750
or I shall throw you in a cell.

617
00:48:38,070 --> 00:48:38,590
Boon!

618
00:48:38,620 --> 00:48:39,850
- My dear Orn!
- Boon!

619
00:48:40,070 --> 00:48:40,670
Orn.

620
00:48:40,700 --> 00:48:41,610
Boon.

621
00:48:46,950 --> 00:48:47,530
There.

622
00:48:48,230 --> 00:48:49,300
You possess a blade as well?

623
00:48:52,280 --> 00:48:53,080
Klao.

624
00:48:53,590 --> 00:48:55,140
You brought such peril upon the household?

625
00:48:56,850 --> 00:48:58,640
I shall report this to His Excellency.

626
00:49:19,760 --> 00:49:20,600
Phop.

627
00:49:21,730 --> 00:49:23,590
I entrusted the manor to your care.

628
00:49:23,980 --> 00:49:25,560
How, then, did it come to this state?

629
00:49:27,040 --> 00:49:27,740
Uh...

630
00:49:28,500 --> 00:49:30,400
I sincerely apologize, Aunt.

631
00:49:31,170 --> 00:49:31,980
I...

632
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:33,840
I... I promise that

633
00:49:33,920 --> 00:49:35,650
from now on, it shall never happen again.

634
00:49:35,820 --> 00:49:36,660
Never again

635
00:49:37,110 --> 00:49:39,060
shall there be such an incident,

636
00:49:40,790 --> 00:49:41,920
for you

637
00:49:42,710 --> 00:49:45,110
shall no longer remain in my household!

638
00:49:45,140 --> 00:49:45,960
Father!

639
00:49:46,100 --> 00:49:47,380
My decision is final.

640
00:49:48,390 --> 00:49:50,090
You squandered your days away

641
00:49:51,000 --> 00:49:53,060
and wasted yourself at the House of Pleasure

642
00:49:53,290 --> 00:49:54,440
for days on end!

643
00:49:54,940 --> 00:49:56,360
It was already unacceptable!

644
00:49:57,080 --> 00:49:58,720
Yet you brought a threat to our household.

645
00:50:00,670 --> 00:50:02,770
Your one true brother's life
was almost in jeopardy,

646
00:50:02,790 --> 00:50:03,360
Phop!

647
00:50:03,640 --> 00:50:05,560
Boon is not my true brother, Father.

648
00:50:10,670 --> 00:50:11,440
Phop.

649
00:50:12,280 --> 00:50:15,210
I never raised you to be
disrespectful toward your father

650
00:50:15,380 --> 00:50:16,810
and Lady Bud.

651
00:50:17,820 --> 00:50:18,860
It is you, Aunt Bud,

652
00:50:19,380 --> 00:50:21,080
who brought Cherd
to cause chaos at our manor.

653
00:50:22,180 --> 00:50:24,080
I saw her exchange looks with him
with my own eyes.

654
00:50:28,800 --> 00:50:30,320
Where has it gone,

655
00:50:32,480 --> 00:50:34,070
the ring I bought for you

656
00:50:34,400 --> 00:50:35,880
on the Songkran of yesteryear?

657
00:50:38,160 --> 00:50:39,880
You bestowed the ring on Cherd, did you not?

658
00:50:41,780 --> 00:50:43,480
It served as payment for his misdeeds,

659
00:50:43,950 --> 00:50:45,840
orchestrated to expel Klao from this manor.

660
00:50:47,370 --> 00:50:48,440
Is this true, Lady Bud?

661
00:50:50,870 --> 00:50:51,840
It is not, Your Excellency.

662
00:50:53,290 --> 00:50:54,600
Phop has falsely accused me,

663
00:50:55,360 --> 00:50:57,400
for no other reason than protecting Klao,

664
00:51:01,480 --> 00:51:03,650
- as Phop and Klao are...
- Sister!

665
00:51:05,400 --> 00:51:06,520
A matter such as this,

666
00:51:06,720 --> 00:51:08,640
it is best we let Phop explain everything.

667
00:51:11,660 --> 00:51:12,920
What is amiss, Phop?

668
00:51:17,070 --> 00:51:19,840
What are you to Klao?!!

669
00:51:46,950 --> 00:51:48,340
I love him

670
00:51:48,790 --> 00:51:50,490
as one would love one's beloved, Father.

671
00:52:14,840 --> 00:52:17,460
I shall deem your words
a temporary lapse of judgment.

672
00:52:19,490 --> 00:52:21,610
Ponder upon this matter
until you are truly certain.

673
00:52:22,830 --> 00:52:25,360
I have never been more certain, Father.

674
00:52:28,790 --> 00:52:30,200
I love Klao,

675
00:52:31,390 --> 00:52:33,420
and my love for him
is no different from yours for Mother.

676
00:52:35,920 --> 00:52:36,680
Phop.

677
00:52:38,540 --> 00:52:39,970
I beg of you,

678
00:52:40,930 --> 00:52:43,200
say no more than this for your sake.

679
00:52:44,870 --> 00:52:46,370
No good

680
00:52:48,350 --> 00:52:50,040
can come from two men being together.

681
00:52:56,260 --> 00:52:57,760
Yet both of you,

682
00:52:59,420 --> 00:53:01,170
though a man and a woman,

683
00:53:01,390 --> 00:53:03,680
have hardly had a love that is any better.

684
00:53:10,460 --> 00:53:12,560
My heart belongs to Dear Klao and him alone.

685
00:53:18,280 --> 00:53:20,840
And I shall never take another
into my heart, as you have done.

686
00:53:24,720 --> 00:53:25,520
Phop.

687
00:53:28,240 --> 00:53:29,420
Cease this.

688
00:53:37,490 --> 00:53:39,560
I shall find another place for you.

689
00:53:41,710 --> 00:53:42,920
Once found,

690
00:53:44,550 --> 00:53:47,060
pack your belongings and be gone from here.

691
00:53:52,980 --> 00:53:53,780
Father!!

692
00:53:54,600 --> 00:53:56,060
I shall not accept this.

693
00:54:08,020 --> 00:54:08,840
Mother!

694
00:54:11,490 --> 00:54:13,420
I beg of you,
speak to Father on my behalf.

695
00:54:16,760 --> 00:54:17,780
Mother!

696
00:54:26,110 --> 00:54:26,960
Phop.

697
00:54:28,440 --> 00:54:30,760
Your father shall never comprehend
a matter such as this.

698
00:54:41,050 --> 00:54:42,130
Klao,

699
00:54:44,900 --> 00:54:47,000
I have never despised you.

700
00:54:48,280 --> 00:54:51,120
I have always cherished you with affection,
as if you were my own child.

701
00:54:56,100 --> 00:54:57,110
But I...

702
00:54:58,760 --> 00:55:00,360
I am unable to accept it,

703
00:55:01,340 --> 00:55:02,600
at least

704
00:55:05,870 --> 00:55:07,040
for the time being.

705
00:55:10,430 --> 00:55:11,360
Phop.

706
00:55:12,790 --> 00:55:14,680
Kindly look upon me with understanding.

707
00:56:10,910 --> 00:56:12,900
Weep no more, my dearest heart.

708
00:56:18,970 --> 00:56:20,550
Even if everything ends up like this,

709
00:56:22,690 --> 00:56:25,450
I promise my love for you shall never fade.

710
00:56:29,700 --> 00:56:30,510
I know.

711
00:56:33,230 --> 00:56:35,890
I do not wish to let them down,

712
00:56:39,020 --> 00:56:41,370
but I, too, do not wish
to give up on our love.

713
00:57:01,980 --> 00:57:03,280
If such is the case,

714
00:57:06,100 --> 00:57:08,920
I call upon the Goddess of Water
to bear witness to my vow.

715
00:57:12,510 --> 00:57:14,440
I shall carve our path with my hands.

716
00:57:16,820 --> 00:57:19,850
Should Father truly
cast you out of the manor,

717
00:57:23,210 --> 00:57:24,980
I shall forsake all and depart with you.

718
00:57:27,480 --> 00:57:29,830
But they are your parents.

719
00:57:34,040 --> 00:57:35,980
Do you think
you can leave them behind that easily?

720
00:57:39,670 --> 00:57:41,090
It would not be easy,

721
00:57:46,090 --> 00:57:48,240
but it would be harder for me to let you go.

722
00:57:52,950 --> 00:57:54,480
I promise you

723
00:57:57,400 --> 00:58:00,080
I shall let nothing tear us apart.

724
00:58:03,490 --> 00:58:05,090
Everything shall resolve itself

725
00:58:06,700 --> 00:58:09,690
as long as we have each other, as we do now.

726
00:58:09,750 --> 00:58:16,490
♫I don't wish for the tomorrow with you gone♫

727
00:58:16,610 --> 00:58:19,750
♫I'm not ready to lose you,
having everything come undone♫

728
00:58:19,770 --> 00:58:22,740
♫I don't want to see you fade away from me♫

729
00:58:22,770 --> 00:58:29,610
♫I wish the ticking clock would forever freeze♫

730
00:58:29,700 --> 00:58:32,830
♫If there was a path I could take,♫

731
00:58:32,860 --> 00:58:36,100
♫Could it make us be together instead?♫

732
00:58:36,120 --> 00:58:38,340
♫I would embrace you tightly,♫

733
00:58:38,360 --> 00:58:40,840
♫Not leaving you behind and with nobody♫

734
00:58:41,940 --> 00:58:44,700
So long as Klao's madness

735
00:58:45,110 --> 00:58:46,130
does not subside,

736
00:58:47,430 --> 00:58:49,920
Phop is in no condition to wed.

737
00:58:56,340 --> 00:58:58,070
Therefore, I must postpone the ceremony.

738
00:58:59,770 --> 00:59:02,060
I shall set off to apologize

739
00:59:02,500 --> 00:59:04,270
High Lord Dech Kraisor in person.

740
00:59:08,770 --> 00:59:09,880
A postponement

741
00:59:11,470 --> 00:59:13,620
is nothing but a rejection.

742
00:59:24,550 --> 00:59:25,550
If your love for Klao

743
00:59:26,480 --> 00:59:28,500
is so profound,

744
00:59:32,230 --> 00:59:34,120
then go forth and wed him.

745
00:59:43,080 --> 00:59:45,520
I sincerely apologize, High Lord Horathibodi.

746
00:59:51,320 --> 00:59:53,590
I believe the one you should apologize to

747
00:59:55,540 --> 00:59:57,090
is Lady Varna,

748
00:59:57,580 --> 00:59:58,560
Lord Phop.

749
01:00:05,080 --> 01:00:06,080
Lady Varna,

750
01:00:06,810 --> 01:00:08,140
it is my fault.

751
01:00:09,000 --> 01:00:10,430
I beg for your forgiveness.

752
01:00:13,120 --> 01:00:14,580
Think no more of it, my Lord.

753
01:00:16,340 --> 01:00:17,690
I understand that

754
01:00:18,600 --> 01:00:21,560
your heart is not captivated by my presence.

755
01:00:22,620 --> 01:00:23,810
Lady Varna.

756
01:00:24,330 --> 01:00:25,800
Blame not yourself, I beg.

757
01:00:26,770 --> 01:00:28,600
You are flawless in every way.

758
01:00:28,790 --> 01:00:30,880
The fault lies with Phop and me.

759
01:00:32,430 --> 01:00:34,360
It is no one's fault.

760
01:00:35,140 --> 01:00:36,530
In truth,

761
01:00:37,980 --> 01:00:40,180
I must convey my gratitude to Klao.

762
01:00:40,950 --> 01:00:42,800
He made me realize that

763
01:00:43,770 --> 01:00:46,150
I need not be anyone's wife

764
01:00:47,580 --> 01:00:49,380
to possess my own worth.

765
01:00:55,890 --> 01:00:57,480
Utter madness.

766
01:00:58,740 --> 01:00:59,590
The man

767
01:01:00,360 --> 01:01:02,560
refuses to wed
out of concern for his brother,

768
01:01:04,400 --> 01:01:05,520
whilst the lady

769
01:01:06,100 --> 01:01:08,790
possesses no desire to be any man's wife.

770
01:01:11,850 --> 01:01:12,880
If such is the case,

771
01:01:14,500 --> 01:01:15,440
I shall take my leave.

772
01:01:16,060 --> 01:01:19,560
Let us confer upon the opium case
at a later hour, High Lord.

773
01:01:43,710 --> 01:01:45,480
Fortunate that Lady Varna understood.

774
01:01:46,250 --> 01:01:48,430
And it was a blessing
that it was the High Lord,

775
01:01:48,460 --> 01:01:49,920
Lady Varna's uncle.

776
01:01:51,610 --> 01:01:53,640
Had it been High Lord Dech Kraisor
in his place,

777
01:01:55,030 --> 01:01:57,440
the altercation would have escalated
far beyond that.

778
01:02:01,470 --> 01:02:02,700
It was because of me.

779
01:02:04,190 --> 01:02:06,180
I caused you and your parents

780
01:02:06,880 --> 01:02:08,420
so much trouble.

781
01:02:22,020 --> 01:02:23,000
No, you did not.

782
01:02:24,450 --> 01:02:27,490
It was Father who wished
to betroth me to her,

783
01:02:28,590 --> 01:02:30,400
against my own will entirely.

784
01:02:32,740 --> 01:02:34,300
I did not dare to oppose him,

785
01:02:35,530 --> 01:02:38,770
as this is how he raised me
since I was a little child.

786
01:02:41,900 --> 01:02:43,570
Then, you accepted my love.

787
01:02:54,700 --> 01:02:56,400
Stay by my side
for all the days to come, Klao.

788
01:02:58,670 --> 01:03:00,200
I have no wish to go anywhere else, do I?

789
01:03:02,760 --> 01:03:03,760
Indeed.

790
01:03:04,610 --> 01:03:06,200
Do not seek Cherd out either.

791
01:03:08,100 --> 01:03:10,080
He had the audacity to march into our manor.

792
01:03:12,100 --> 01:03:15,190
Regardless of his conspiring with Aunt Bud,

793
01:03:16,300 --> 01:03:17,800
his insolence is beyond measure.

794
01:03:20,690 --> 01:03:22,400
Should he find you out there after this,

795
01:03:23,580 --> 01:03:25,230
he would certainly not spare you.

796
01:03:29,940 --> 01:03:32,390
But it is guaranteed that
Cherd has a wound on his arm.

797
01:03:32,560 --> 01:03:33,660
You saw it, too.

798
01:03:34,880 --> 01:03:36,550
But why did your subordinate report that

799
01:03:36,880 --> 01:03:38,470
he was not found among the patrol units.

800
01:03:39,320 --> 01:03:40,440
Do you think it is peculiar?

801
01:03:44,590 --> 01:03:47,700
Kla has indeed been keeping
a close watch on Cherd.

802
01:03:49,580 --> 01:03:51,060
He and I have long been working together.

803
01:03:52,620 --> 01:03:53,760
He can be trusted.

804
01:04:05,230 --> 01:04:05,910
Mm.

805
01:05:21,080 --> 01:05:26,120
[Execute the plan at once]

806
01:05:28,430 --> 01:05:29,160
And

807
01:05:30,730 --> 01:05:32,290
what about the wound on his arm?

808
01:05:33,030 --> 01:05:34,080
What would you say?

809
01:05:38,440 --> 01:05:39,760
We possess no concrete proof.

810
01:05:41,140 --> 01:05:43,070
Some unforeseen accident
might have caused it.

811
01:05:44,590 --> 01:05:46,060
Would not that be a bit of a coincidence?

812
01:05:50,060 --> 01:05:50,990
Anyhow,

813
01:05:52,000 --> 01:05:54,600
I must uncover more of the truth.

814
01:05:55,990 --> 01:05:57,480
If the location that my record mentioned

815
01:05:58,650 --> 01:06:00,280
really is the meeting place,

816
01:06:01,630 --> 01:06:03,620
then I must know where it is.

817
01:06:05,150 --> 01:06:07,740
And Pim's hesitation
and her refusal to speak

818
01:06:08,930 --> 01:06:09,880
signifies that

819
01:06:10,690 --> 01:06:12,220
she knows something.

820
01:06:20,920 --> 01:06:25,140
♫Filled the air with its fragrance,
the star jasmine did,♫

821
01:06:25,380 --> 01:06:27,610
♫As did others of its kind♫

822
01:06:28,440 --> 01:06:34,770
♫The antoka and the perfume plant
bloomed with joy♫

823
01:06:35,360 --> 01:06:39,240
♫Sweet as the very fragrance of my beloved♫

824
01:06:39,600 --> 01:06:44,520
♫Dear the love of my life,♫

825
01:06:44,970 --> 01:06:49,530
♫Your fragrance did I smell,
yet you were nowhere to be seen♫

826
01:06:49,680 --> 01:06:54,400
♫The thorns of longing
are more than I can bear♫

827
01:07:02,390 --> 01:07:04,690
Should your tongue slip,
I shall bring about your demise.

828
01:07:26,960 --> 01:07:28,240
The fifteenth night of the waning moon.

829
01:07:31,490 --> 01:07:33,930
We previously seized the opium at Sam Khok

830
01:07:34,610 --> 01:07:35,870
approximately at this moon phase.

831
01:07:37,980 --> 01:07:39,100
Perchance,

832
01:07:40,070 --> 01:07:43,760
they schedule their illicit shipments
upon this precise night of every month.

833
01:07:45,220 --> 01:07:45,880
And...

834
01:07:46,630 --> 01:07:47,810
That is only a few days away.

835
01:07:49,490 --> 01:07:50,270
Yes.

836
01:07:52,000 --> 01:07:54,320
Should we converge upon
the designated hour and place,

837
01:07:55,940 --> 01:07:57,720
we shall undoubtedly capture Cherd.

838
01:08:01,420 --> 01:08:03,320
Should we manage to capture him,

839
01:08:05,040 --> 01:08:08,040
we might be able to use him to
trace back to the one who framed my father.

840
01:08:10,570 --> 01:08:11,280
Phop!

841
01:08:12,990 --> 01:08:16,560
Tell me everything that you know
about my father.

842
01:08:48,880 --> 01:08:50,350
That is the son of High Lord Sintaranurak.

843
01:08:50,370 --> 01:08:51,600
It is said that he is effeminate.

844
01:08:51,620 --> 01:08:52,439
How peculiar.

845
01:08:52,550 --> 01:08:53,560
Look at how you protect one another.

846
01:08:53,600 --> 01:08:56,470
One might think you are husband and wife.
Or is it merely a passing fancy?

847
01:08:59,960 --> 01:09:00,770
Dear Klao.

848
01:09:01,290 --> 01:09:03,520
I have secured for you
a position in the official service of Lavo.

849
01:09:03,920 --> 01:09:05,840
Gather your belongings
and depart on the morrow.

850
01:09:06,040 --> 01:09:06,729
But...

851
01:09:07,189 --> 01:09:08,700
I fear I am unable to depart.

852
01:09:09,590 --> 01:09:12,000
You wish for us to escort you into...

853
01:09:12,170 --> 01:09:13,700
the House of Pleasure?

854
01:09:13,830 --> 01:09:14,569
Yes.

855
01:09:14,640 --> 01:09:16,290
Tonight is the fifteenth night
of the waning moon.

856
01:09:16,319 --> 01:09:19,439
- Cherd should smuggle opium tonight, if true.
- Pim!

857
01:09:22,960 --> 01:09:26,800
Grant me your forgiveness,
I beg of you, Klao.

858
01:09:27,350 --> 01:09:34,090
♫I wish the ticking clock would forever freeze♫

859
01:09:34,170 --> 01:09:37,340
♫If there was a path I could take,♫

860
01:09:37,359 --> 01:09:40,590
♫Could it make us be together instead?♫

861
01:09:40,630 --> 01:09:42,870
♫I would embrace you tightly,♫

862
01:09:42,890 --> 01:09:47,010
♫Not leaving you behind and with nobody♫

863
01:09:56,500 --> 01:10:03,320
♫I wish the ticking clock would forever freeze♫

864
01:10:03,360 --> 01:10:06,500
♫If there was a path I could take,♫

865
01:10:06,520 --> 01:10:09,780
♫Could it make us be together instead?♫

866
01:10:09,840 --> 01:10:12,030
♫I would embrace you tightly,♫

867
01:10:12,050 --> 01:10:16,590
♫Not leaving you behind and with nobody♫

